# spec/dummy host app — everything generated by `bin/reset-dummy` is
# transient pre-v1. Source of truth for schema lives in
# lib/generators/curator/install/templates/; contributors regenerate the
# dummy locally. Re-evaluate committing these at v1 once templates stabilize.
